"```sql\nSELECT AVG(district.A15) AS average_crimes_1995\nFROM district\nJOIN account ON district.district_id = account.district_id\nWHERE district.A15 > 4000\n  AND account.date >= '1997-01-01'\nGROUP BY district.A3;\n```\n\nThis SQL query calculates the average number of crimes committed in 1995 (`A15`) for regions (`A3`) where the number of crimes exceeds 4000 and there are accounts opened starting from the year 1997. The query joins the `district` and `account` tables using the `district_id` foreign key relationship and filters the results based on the specified conditions."